trans-unit.source: The exception that is thrown when an attempt to access a file that does not exist on disk fails.
trans-unit.target: 尝试访问磁盘上不存在的文件失败时引发的异常。

trans-unit.source: `FileNotFoundException` uses the HRESULT COR_E_FILENOTFOUND which has the value 0x80070002.
trans-unit.target: `FileNotFoundException` 使用具有值 0x80070002 HRESULT COR_E_FILENOTFOUND。

trans-unit.source: If your code does not have <xref:System.Security.Permissions.FileIOPermissionAttribute.PathDiscovery%2A> permission, the error message for this exception may only contain file or directory names instead of fully qualified paths.
trans-unit.target: 如果你的代码不具有<xref:System.Security.Permissions.FileIOPermissionAttribute.PathDiscovery%2A>权限，错误消息，此异常可能仅包含文件或目录的名称，而不是完全限定路径。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> class with optional message string and inner <see langword="Exception" /> reference.
trans-unit.target: 用可选消息字符串和内部 <see langword="Exception" /> 引用初始化 <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> class with its message string set to a system-supplied message.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> 类的新实例，将其消息字符串设置为系统提供的消息。

trans-unit.source: This constructor initializes the <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A> property of the new instance to a system-supplied message that describes the error, such as "Could not find the specified file."
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数初始化<xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A>属性的新实例为系统提供的消息的描述错误，如"找不到指定的文件。"

trans-unit.source: This message takes into account the current system culture.
trans-unit.target: 此消息将当前系统区域性考虑在内。

trans-unit.source: A description of the error.
trans-unit.target: 错误说明。

trans-unit.source: The content of <c>message</c> is intended to be understood by humans.
trans-unit.target: 消息的内容被设计为人可理解的形式<c></c>。

trans-unit.source: The caller of this constructor is required to ensure that this string has been localized for the current system culture.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数的调用方需要确保此字符串已针对当前系统区域性进行了本地化。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> class with a specified error message.
trans-unit.target: 用指定的错误消息初始化 <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: This constructor initializes the <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A> property of the new instance using `message`.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数初始化<xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A>属性的新实例使用`message`。

trans-unit.source: An object that holds the serialized object data about the exception being thrown.
trans-unit.target: 保存有关所引发异常的序列化对象数据的对象。

trans-unit.source: An object that contains contextual information about the source or destination.
trans-unit.target: 一个包含有关源或目标的上下文信息的对象。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> class with the specified serialization and context information.
trans-unit.target: 用指定的序列化和上下文信息初始化 <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: A description of the error.
trans-unit.target: 错误说明。

trans-unit.source: The content of <c>message</c> is intended to be understood by humans.
trans-unit.target: 消息的内容被设计为人可理解的形式<c></c>。

trans-unit.source: The caller of this constructor is required to ensure that this string has been localized for the current system culture.
trans-unit.target: 此构造函数的调用方需要确保此字符串已针对当前系统区域性进行了本地化。

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
trans-unit.target: 导致当前异常的异常。

trans-unit.source: If the <c>innerException</c> parameter is not <see langword="null" />, the current exception is raised in a <see langword="catch" /> block that handles the inner exception.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <c>innerException</c> 参数不为 <see langword="null" />，则当前异常会在处理内部异常的 <see langword="catch" /> 块中引发。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> class with a specified error message and a reference to the inner exception that is the cause of this exception.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的错误消息和对作为此异常原因的内部异常的引用来初始化 <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: An exception that is thrown as a direct result of a previous exception should include a reference to the previous exception in the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 因前一个异常而直接引发的异常应在 <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> 属性中包含对前一个异常的引用。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is passed into the constructor, or `null` if the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property does not supply the inner exception value to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> 属性返回的值与传递到构造函数中的值相同；或者，如果 `null` 属性没有向构造函数提供内部异常值，则为 <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>。

trans-unit.target: 包含无效图像的文件的全名。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> class with a specified error message, and the file name that cannot be found.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定错误信息和找不到的文件名来初始化 <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The constructor initializes the <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A> property of the new instance using `message` and the <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.FileName%2A> property using `fileName`.
trans-unit.target: 构造函数初始化<xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A>属性的新实例使用`message`和<xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.FileName%2A>属性使用`fileName`。

trans-unit.source: The error message that explains the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: 解释异常原因的错误消息。

trans-unit.source: The full name of the file with the invalid image.
trans-unit.target: 包含无效图像的文件的全名。

trans-unit.source: The exception that is the cause of the current exception.
trans-unit.target: 导致当前异常的异常。

trans-unit.source: If the <c>innerException</c> parameter is not <see langword="null" />, the current exception is raised in a <see langword="catch" /> block that handles the inner exception.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <c>innerException</c> 参数不为 <see langword="null" />，则当前异常会在处理内部异常的 <see langword="catch" /> 块中引发。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> class with a specified error message, the file name that cannot be found, and a reference to the inner exception that is the cause of this exception.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的错误信息、找不到的文件名和对作为此异常原因的内部异常的引用来初始化 <see cref="T:System.IO.FileNotFoundException" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: An exception that is thrown as a direct result of a previous exception should include a reference to the previous exception in the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 因前一个异常而直接引发的异常应在 <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> 属性中包含对前一个异常的引用。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property returns the same value that is passed into the constructor, or `null` if the <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> property does not supply the inner exception value to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A> 属性返回的值与传递到构造函数中的值相同；或者，如果 `null` 属性没有向构造函数提供内部异常值，则为 <xref:System.Exception.InnerException%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Gets the log file that describes why loading of an assembly failed.
trans-unit.target: 获取日志文件，该文件描述加载程序集失败的原因。

trans-unit.source: The errors reported by the assembly cache.
trans-unit.target: 由程序集缓存报告的错误。

trans-unit.source: The caller does not have the required permission.
trans-unit.target: 调用方没有所要求的权限。

trans-unit.source: to provide evidence and view and modify policy.
trans-unit.target: 若要提供证据以及查看和修改策略。

trans-unit.source: requires full trust for the immediate caller.
trans-unit.target: 需要完全信任直接调用方。

trans-unit.source: Gets the error message that explains the reason for the exception.
trans-unit.target: 获取解释异常原因的错误消息。

trans-unit.source: The error message.
trans-unit.target: 错误消息。

trans-unit.source: If no message was supplied to the constructor for the current exception, this property returns a system-supplied error message.
trans-unit.target: 如果为当前异常的构造函数不硅酮任何消息，此属性将返回系统提供的错误消息。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.IO.FileLoadException.FileName%2A> property is not `null`, the message includes the file name.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.IO.FileLoadException.FileName%2A>属性不是`null`，该消息包含的文件名称。

trans-unit.source: This property is read-only.
trans-unit.target: 此属性是只读的。

trans-unit.source: Returns the fully qualified name of this exception and possibly the error message, the name of the inner exception, and the stack trace.
trans-unit.target: 返回该异常的完全限定名，还可能返回错误消息、内部异常的名称和堆栈跟踪。

trans-unit.source: The fully qualified name of this exception and possibly the error message, the name of the inner exception, and the stack trace.
trans-unit.target: 该异常的完全限定名，还可能是错误消息、内部异常的名称和堆栈跟踪。

trans-unit.source: This method overrides <xref:System.Object.ToString%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法重写 <xref:System.Object.ToString%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The string representation returned by this method includes the name of the exception, the value of the <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A> property, the result of calling ToString on the inner exception, the value of the <xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.FileName%2A> property, and the result of calling <xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法返回的字符串表示形式包括的异常的值名称<xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.Message%2A>属性、 对内部异常的值调用 ToString 的结果<xref:System.IO.FileNotFoundException.FileName%2A>属性，并调用的结果<xref:System.Environment.StackTrace%2A>.

trans-unit.source: If any of these members is a null reference, its value is not included in the returned string.
trans-unit.target: 如果任何这些成员为空引用，其值不是包括在返回的字符串。
